{"tid":2277158,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"駐軍再拍片 裝甲車闖鬧市","createTime":"2020-11-08T09:08:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T09:08:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5b08f21703359ad2b29ed91fc18145f72540fcf3","tid":2277158,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T09:08:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201108/RUU2DQEUHZD57IIJ5CMO6VBOLI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201108%2FRUU2DQEUHZD57IIJ5CMO6VBOLI%2F&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq704axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=8b347d25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201108%2FRUU2DQEUHZD57IIJ5CMO6VBOLI%2F&h=49562011\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201108/RUU2DQEUHZD57IIJ5CMO6VBOLI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n駐軍再拍片 裝甲車闖鬧市<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6S6uaOWke6F_tSNJhCQK59o4b14=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6VGVQ7IJHFBSVP4QFQZSGMQNXU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6S6uaOWke6F_tSNJhCQK59o4b14%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6VGVQ7IJHFBSVP4QFQZSGMQNXU.jpg&h=aa40e1d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■宣傳影片中，駐港解放軍的裝甲車途經粉嶺。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】解放軍駐港部隊又拍片放上網，今次主題是裝甲訓練。中國新聞網報道，駐港解放軍近期在港訓練場組織了一次裝步分隊野外駐訓。演練武器包括導彈、火炮、步槍、手槍及煙霧彈，提升部隊履行香港防務能力。<br />\n<br />\n片段顯示，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n時事評論員劉銳紹稱，駐軍宣傳是官方意願，希望在港建立威信，然而解放軍在港的行動始終予港人高壓統治的感覺，宣傳影片未必能改善軍隊形象，「拍幾多片都係冇用」。<br />\n<br />\n熟知國情的浸大新聞系高級講師呂秉權則指出，影片中駐軍雖經過鬧市，但行動較為低調，「佢可以從車伸槍出嚟，但段片冇影到」。他相信中共研判《國安法》下，香港民間仍有「唔少挑釁」，因此發放影片強調軍隊隨時可到市區執行軍事行動。"}]}